Name: REFERENCE POINT TYPE
Explanation: A TYPE OF REFERENCE OR CONTROL POINT USED IN DATA LINK AND/OR MARITIME AND AIR TACTICAL OPERATIONS.

Name: CONTROL POINT TYPE
Explanation: THE CODE USED TO SPECIFY THE TYPE OF CONTROL POINT.

Name: DATA LINK REFERENCE POINT TYPE
Explanation: THE TYPE OF SYSTEM REFERENCE POINT USED BY A SPECIFIC TACTICAL DATA LINK NETWORK.
